      <title>PNC 净利息收入下滑，贷款增长依然疲软</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/pnc-net-interest-income-misses-estimates-with-loan-growth-muted</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PNC Financial Services Group Inc.第一季度净利息收入未达到预期，这表明这家总部位于匹兹堡的银行仍在继续应对贷款增长放缓的问题。]]></description>
